<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 24. Bracon (Uncobracon) eurysulcatus sp. nov., ♀, holotype. a. Fore wing; b. Hind wing; c. Mesosoma, lateral view; d. Mesosoma, dorsal view; e. Metasoma, dorsal view; f. Hind leg, lateral view; g. Head, front view; h. Head, dorsal view; i. head, lateral view; j. Mandible, lateral view; k. First metasomal tergite, dorsal view; l. Apex of antenna; m. Apex of ovipositor, lateral view." , "Figure 25. Bracon (Uncobracon) longwangshanensis sp. nov., ♀, holotype, habitus lateral." , "Figure 27. Bracon (Uncobracon) pappi Tobias, 2000, ♀, habitus lateral." , "Figure 28. Bracon (Uncobracon) pappi Tobias, 2000. ♀. a. Fore wing; b. Hind wing; c. Mesosoma, lateral view; d. Mesosoma, dorsal view; e. Metasoma, dorsal view; f. Hind leg, lateral view; g. Head, front view; h. Head, dorsal view; i. Head, lateral view; j. Mandible, lateral view; k. First metasomal tergite, dorsal view; l. Apex of antenna; m. Apex of ovipositor, lateral view." , "Figure 29. Bracon (Uncobracon) tricoloratus Tobias, 2000, ♀, habitus lateral." , "Figure 26. Bracon (Uncobracon) longwangshanensis sp. nov., ♀, holotype. a. Fore wing; b. Hind wing; c. Mesosoma, lateral view; d. Mesosoma, dorsal view; e. Metasoma, dorsal view; f. Hind leg, lateral view; g. Head, front view; h. Head, dorsal view; i. Head, lateral view; j. Mandible, lateral view; k. First metasomal tergite, dorsal view; l. Apex of antenna." , "Figure 23. Bracon (Uncobracon) eurysulcatus sp. nov., ♀, holotype, habitus lateral." , "Figure 30. Bracon (Uncobracon) tricoloratus Tobias, 2000. ♀. a. Fore wing; b. Hind wing; c. Mesosoma, lateral view; d. Mesosoma, dorsal view; e. Metasoma, dorsal view; f. Hind leg, lateral view; g. Head, front view; h. Head, dorsal view; i. Head, lateral view; j. Mandible, lateral view; k. First metasomal tergite, dorsal view; l. Apex of ovipositor, lateral view." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/477237" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/477234" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/477235" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/477238" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/477239" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/477233" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/477240" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/477236" .

